            "questionText": "Assume a nuclear power plant reactor initially contains $!$1000\\,kg$!$ of uranium-235 and operates for 24 hours, consuming $!$1\\,g$!$ of uranium-235 per hour. What is the remaining mass of uranium-235 in the reactor at the end of the 24-hour period (in $!$kg$!$)?",
